title: PraxisApp - Urologie
description:
Your direct line to your urologist or your urologist!
Choose your practice or your physician / doctor from out of the Doctors. ** Only doctors who have registered for this service, can be found in the doctor's list. **
If you have registered with your data, your doctor or health care professional may send you general and personal information. Via the message function you receive messages via push quickly and directly to your phone.

With the PraxisApp "Urology" you get:

• General and personal messages from your doctor
• appointment reminders, which has set for you by your doctor
• Individual therapy reminders in consultation with your doctor
• Reminder of annual cancer early detection
• Video consultation with your doctor (only if your doctor offers this service for you)
• Current information on Urology - published in cooperation with the Professional Association of German Urologists e.V. (BVDU)
